1.) if the xampp is running, check the port and ssl in config: (should be default params)
2.) type 'ngrok http 80' to establish the connection between devices
3.) check the firewall 'sudo ufw status'
4.) if it's not connecting via ssh tunnel => sudo ufw allow 80/tcp comment 'Allow Apache HTTP'
5.) check the number of connection via tcp/ssh tunnel => sudo ufw status numbered




take note: 
- The connection between devices should be the same as well as the wifi IP4
- sudo ufw enable
- systemctl status ufw.service

>> sudo ufw default deny incoming

Default incoming policy changed to 'deny'
(be sure to update your rules accordingly)

>> grep IPV6 /etc/default/ufw

IPV6=yes


>> sudo ufw allow ssh

Rule added
Rule added (v6)

>> sudo ufw allow 443
Rule added
Rule added (v6)

>> sudo ufw allow 80
Rule added
Rule added (v6)



